Cierra Kaler-Jones (amụrụ na Mee 29, n'afọ 1993) bụ onye America mara mma nke e chiri Miss New Jersey n'afọ 2014. Ọ bụ onye Afrịka nke abụọ meriri Miss New Jersey mgbe Suzette Charles gasịrị n'afọ 1983
Ihe nketa ya gụnyere ndị Amerịka, Irish, Filipino na German.

Kaler-Jones si Galloway Township, New Jersey ma gaa Absegami High School. Kaler-Jones bụ onye gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Rutgers ebe ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Social Work na itinye uche na Women's & Gender Studies, na Critical & Comparative Race & Ethnic Studies

Ọ gara Rutgers dị ka nwa akwụkwọ kọleji ọgbọ mbụ. Na mgbakwunye, ọ nọrọ afọ atọ mbụ ya na Rutgers na Rutgers University otu na agba egwú  ma rụọ ọrụ dị ka onye enyemaka nyocha na Rutgers School of Social Work ma tinye aka na ACLU nke New Jersey na ngalaba ikpe ziri ezi nke ụlọ ọrụ onye ọka iwu steeti.
Ọ bụ nwa akwụkwọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ ugbu a na Education and Human Development

Kaler-Jones bụbu Miss Atlantic County, Miss Northern Lakes, Miss Cape Shores, na Miss Coastal Shore. N'ịza ajụjụ banyere mkpa nke asọmpi Miss America, o kwuru, sị: "Gịnị dị mkpa karịa nwanyị dị ike?" A kpọrọ ya Miss New Jersey n'afo 2014 na June 14 na ikpo okwu: "Empowering Today's Youth Through Arts Education." Nkà ya bụ ịgba egwu nke oge a na-eme onwe ya na "Listen" nke Beyonce. (Ọ bụ onye otu Rutgers Dance Team). Kaler-Jones sọrọ mpi n'otu akụkụ n'ihi na ụfọdụ ndị gwara ya na ọ "enweghị ike ịbụ Miss New Jersey n'ihi na anaghị m ele anya n'ụzọ ụfọdụ ma ọ bụ na-adabaghị n'ụdị ụfọdụ" ma ọ na-eche ihe kpatara na ọ gaghị.
